---
import Gear from "../assets/icons/gear.svg";
import Idea from "../assets/icons/idea.svg";
import Read from "../assets/icons/read.svg";
import Rf from "../assets/icons/rf.svg";
---

<section class="feature">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What can Limulus AI do?</h2>
    <p class="feature-subtitle">
      Limulus AI is not a chatbot. It is an intelligent customer service system
      that:
    </p>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-image">
          <img src={Idea.src} alt="Analysis" />
        </div>
        <p class="p-title">Understands customer intent</p>
        <p class="p--small">
          Thanks to language models, Limulus AI analyzes requests in natural
          language (text, voice, forms), recognizing both the context and the
          user’s goal.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-image">
          <img src={Gear.src} alt="Automation" />
        </div>
        <p class="p-title">Automates actions</p>
        <p class="p--small">
          The system independently performs operations such as password reset,
          status change, account creation, or refunds through integration with
          your systems’ APIs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-image">
          <img src={Rf.src} alt="Omnichannel support" />
        </div>
        <p class="p-title">Supports multiple channels</p>
        <p class="p--small">
          Works in an omnichannel model: email, chat, SMS, forms — ensuring
          consistent support regardless of the channel.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-image">
          <img src={Read.src} alt="Knowledge base" />
        </div>
        <p class="p-title">Uses your knowledge base</p>
        <p class="p--small">
          Provides precise answers to customer questions based on your data,
          instructions, and FAQs — without the need to “train” it from scratch.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
